               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dāwit “Psalter” (fols. 2r-150rb)&#xD;
I-1) Mazmura Dāwit “Psalms of David” (fols. 2r-117r) &#xD;
I-2) Maḥālǝya nabiyāt “The Canticles of the Prophets” (fols. 117r-129r) &#xD;
I-3) Maḥālǝya maḥālǝy “Song of Songs” (fols. 129r-135v) &#xD;
I-4) Wǝddāse Māryām “Praise of Mary” (fols. 136r-150vb) &#xD;
I-5) ʾAnqaṣa bǝrhān “The Gate of Light” (fols. 145rb-149rb) &#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-4.</summary>
